1
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:11,880
What happened?

2
00:00:11,550 --> 00:00:18,180
[1995]

3
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:13,160
Just look at what you've done to my son!

4
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:13,830
Apologize!

5
00:00:13,830 --> 00:00:14,930
-You must apologize!
-Brother is there.

6
00:00:14,930 --> 00:00:15,590
Okay, okay.

7
00:00:16,710 --> 00:00:18,000
Sir! Sir!

8
00:00:18,570 --> 00:00:19,800
Don't get physical.
Let's talk this through.

9
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:21,510
Adults shouldn't bully children!

10
00:00:21,510 --> 00:00:23,440
Look how badly he's beaten my son!

11
00:00:23,470 --> 00:00:24,400
Everyone, look!

12
00:00:24,670 --> 00:00:25,390
What's wrong with saying that?

13
00:00:25,390 --> 00:00:26,440
Isn't that the truth?

14
00:00:26,440 --> 00:00:27,510
You were born but not properly raised!

15
00:00:27,510 --> 00:00:28,830
Look how viciously you beat him!

16
00:00:28,830 --> 00:00:30,290
Alright, let's calm down.

17
00:00:30,430 --> 00:00:32,020
We'll cover the medical bills.

18
00:00:32,020 --> 00:00:34,000
Let's try to talk this through, okay?

19
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:35,540
If Jiang Cheng doesn't kneel down
and apologize today,

20
00:00:35,540 --> 00:00:36,440
this isn't over!

21
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:37,080
Not over!

22
00:00:37,100 --> 00:00:38,360
So what if you're a cop?

23
00:00:38,450 --> 00:00:39,600
Come on.

24
00:00:40,070 --> 00:00:41,320
I am a cop, yes,

25
00:00:41,510 --> 00:00:43,300
but I am also his father!

26
00:00:43,560 --> 00:00:44,350
From today on,

27
00:00:44,350 --> 00:00:45,550
Jiang Cheng is my son!

28
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:48,060
None of you shall say
he has no parents again!

29
00:00:56,470 --> 00:00:59,870
[Young Jiang Cheng]

30
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:08,950
Brother!

31
00:01:08,980 --> 00:01:09,800
Let's make a toast!

32
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:11,060
Sure, sister. Come on.

33
00:01:11,060 --> 00:01:12,220
Me too! Me too!

34
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:13,060
Come on.

35
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:13,800
Cheers!

36
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,150
Brother!

37
00:01:21,220 --> 00:01:21,680
Come on.

38
00:01:23,730 --> 00:01:24,340
Brother,

39
00:01:24,370 --> 00:01:25,570
me too!

40
00:01:26,350 --> 00:01:26,810
Come on.

41
00:01:27,070 --> 00:01:28,400
Brother, lift me up too.

42
00:01:29,970 --> 00:01:30,560
Brother!

43
00:01:30,910 --> 00:01:31,510
Brother!

44
00:01:32,140 --> 00:01:32,600
Come on!

45
00:01:33,479 --> 00:01:34,810
You need to lose weight.

46
00:01:35,780 --> 00:01:36,979
He's my brother.

47
00:01:37,090 --> 00:01:38,690
Your brother is my brother.

48
00:01:39,220 --> 00:01:40,700
No, he's mine alone!

49
00:01:40,789 --> 00:01:41,560
Stingy.

50
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:42,350
Chuan,

51
00:01:42,570 --> 00:01:43,850
let's become sworn siblings.

52
00:01:43,850 --> 00:01:44,280
Sure.

53
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:45,460
You're the eldest.

54
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,590
I'm second,

55
00:01:47,170 --> 00:01:48,170
Zhan Wei third,

56
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:49,320
Yan Bin fourth,

57
00:01:50,229 --> 00:01:51,570
and that makes you fifth.

58
00:01:51,570 --> 00:01:52,050
No,

59
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,450
I don't want to be fifth.

60
00:01:53,509 --> 00:01:54,890
-You're fifth!
-Fifth!

61
00:01:54,920 --> 00:02:00,850
-Fifth!
-Fifth!

62
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:29,000
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

63
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:31,820
[Episode 12]

64
00:03:34,180 --> 00:03:35,010
Hansheng.

65
00:03:42,870 --> 00:03:44,360
Gifts should be returned in kind.

66
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,990
Congratulations on graduating from
the Public Security University.

67
00:03:45,990 --> 00:03:47,220
Come visit whenever you can.

68
00:03:47,220 --> 00:03:48,350
I'll buy you a drink.

69
00:03:51,030 --> 00:03:51,560
Take it.

70
00:03:56,140 --> 00:03:56,770
Thank you.

71
00:04:02,620 --> 00:04:03,550
Jiang Hansheng.

72
00:04:58,930 --> 00:04:59,970
Turns out,

73
00:05:00,210 --> 00:05:04,020
if you want to
get under Officer Jiang's skin,

74
00:05:04,050 --> 00:05:06,930
all it takes is the right girl.

75
00:05:07,450 --> 00:05:09,120
Are you scared,

76
00:05:10,010 --> 00:05:11,240
Officer Jiang?

77
00:05:15,630 --> 00:05:17,270
Hansheng, are you alright?

78
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,480
Let's get out.

79
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,470
There's another way.

80
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,800
What way?

81
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:42,120
During those six days at the warehouse
in the 8/17 Case,

82
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,480
there might be some hidden information

83
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,750
that I missed.

84
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,090
I want to try.

85
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:49,800
How?

86
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:53,960
Hypnosis.

87
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:59,340
What did you dream about just now?

88
00:06:02,190 --> 00:06:03,720
Just some bits of memories.

89
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:09,080
So I was thinking...

90
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:12,180
maybe hypnosis would work.

91
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:13,630
Will that really work?

92
00:06:17,570 --> 00:06:19,330
I can't guarantee we'll find any clues.

93
00:06:19,330 --> 00:06:21,130
I'm not talking about the clues.

94
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,750
I mean you.

95
00:06:25,570 --> 00:06:26,330
Can you

96
00:06:27,210 --> 00:06:28,410
really handle it?

97
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,710
Don't push yourself.

98
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:46,010
I'm not pushing myself.

99
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:48,120
Zhou Jin,

100
00:06:49,670 --> 00:06:51,130
I want to try one more time.

101
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:14,120
Around 2:00 AM this morning,

102
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,290
the police emergency line
received a report:

103
00:07:15,290 --> 00:07:16,800
a silver-gray sedan

104
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,870
suddenly caught fire,

105
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:19,370
veered off the road,
and plunged into a river.

106
00:07:19,370 --> 00:07:20,270
The salvage team is currently

107
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:21,600
searching for the vehicle at the scene.

108
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:23,850
The cause of the accident is
under further investigation.

109
00:07:23,850 --> 00:07:25,170
What's there to watch?

110
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,080
That car is mine.

111
00:07:29,890 --> 00:07:30,940
Your car?

112
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,830
Don't you want to know

113
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:34,159
who was in the car, Boss?

114
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:38,690
I want an explanation.

115
00:07:39,670 --> 00:07:40,480
Your car,

116
00:07:41,990 --> 00:07:43,720
and you're asking me for an explanation?

117
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,159
It's not like I burned it.

118
00:07:46,530 --> 00:07:47,200
You did it?

119
00:07:50,550 --> 00:07:52,480
Why did you have Xiao Mao follow me?

120
00:07:52,580 --> 00:07:53,310
Jiang Cheng,

121
00:07:53,659 --> 00:07:55,790
how dare you talk to our boss like that?

122
00:07:56,430 --> 00:07:57,290
Let him finish.

123
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,040
Boss.

124
00:08:01,060 --> 00:08:03,010
I burned the car with Xiao Mao inside.

125
00:08:03,010 --> 00:08:04,210
I didn't want to do it.

126
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,910
But if I don't assert my authority,

127
00:08:06,910 --> 00:08:09,280
how am I supposed to survive
in this line of work?

128
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:09,970
Cheng,

129
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,350
you need to be clearer.

130
00:08:12,860 --> 00:08:14,270
Otherwise, I won't even know
how to answer...

131
00:08:14,270 --> 00:08:15,160
Boss!

132
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:18,090
Xiao Mao told me everything.

133
00:08:18,090 --> 00:08:19,790
You gave him half a million to follow me

134
00:08:19,790 --> 00:08:21,760
and report all my movements to you.

135
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:26,320
What exactly are you suspecting me of?

136
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,550
The work we do is high-risk.

137
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:48,530
It's natural to be more cautious.

138
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,120
Old Scorpion said

139
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:52,530
he's coming to oversee things in person.

140
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,000
If it were you,

141
00:08:55,030 --> 00:08:55,760
wouldn't you

142
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,750
also be extremely careful?

143
00:08:59,790 --> 00:09:02,650
Put yourself in my shoes,
and you'll understand me.

144
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:03,430
Besides,

145
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:05,780
I'm not just keeping an eye on you.

146
00:09:07,430 --> 00:09:09,090
But I trained Xiao Mao myself.

147
00:09:09,100 --> 00:09:10,900
Didn't I lose Zhengtian too?

148
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,720
Traitors like them

149
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:15,200
deserve to die.

150
00:09:15,830 --> 00:09:16,830
Just think of it

151
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,290
that way.

152
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,200
Boss.

153
00:09:25,980 --> 00:09:27,000
I told you before,

154
00:09:27,020 --> 00:09:29,020
I don't like being falsely accused.

155
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:31,510
I told you on the first day
I started working for you

156
00:09:31,510 --> 00:09:32,420
that I was a cop.

157
00:09:32,730 --> 00:09:34,030
And if that bothered you,

158
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:35,690
you didn't have to bring me in.

159
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:41,100
It has nothing to do with that.

160
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,900
With everything you know now,

161
00:09:42,930 --> 00:09:44,530
if you really wanted me dead,

162
00:09:44,790 --> 00:09:46,450
would I still be sitting here?

163
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:50,120
But Cheng...

164
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:54,520
are you really not
hiding anything from me?

165
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:58,910
Zhou Jin.

166
00:09:59,910 --> 00:10:01,240
That's her name, right?

167
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:09,120
Women are trouble.

168
00:10:16,050 --> 00:10:17,650
Whoever lays a finger on her,

169
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:18,780
I'll go after them.

170
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,120
Jiang Cheng,

171
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:23,130
do you have a death wish?

172
00:10:23,190 --> 00:10:23,980
I said,

173
00:10:24,190 --> 00:10:25,390
whoever lays a finger on her,

174
00:10:25,390 --> 00:10:26,450
I'll go after them.

175
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:27,680
I mean what I say.

176
00:10:30,070 --> 00:10:30,790
Love.

177
00:10:31,410 --> 00:10:33,570
Now that is what true love looks like.

178
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,360
Well, at this point,

179
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:41,020
I've got nothing left to hide.

180
00:10:42,850 --> 00:10:44,570
Back then, she was the one
who had me hauled away naked

181
00:10:44,570 --> 00:10:46,370
by the Public Security Brigade.

182
00:10:46,370 --> 00:10:48,100
Do you know what that felt like?

183
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,360
Even today,

184
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:51,360
she still looks at me like I'm trash.

185
00:10:52,370 --> 00:10:53,080
Boss,

186
00:10:53,570 --> 00:10:55,200
when we're out here in this game,

187
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,800
we can't just be after money.

188
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:59,450
We've got to earn some respect too, right?

189
00:11:01,150 --> 00:11:02,200
So how do you plan

190
00:11:03,660 --> 00:11:04,940
to earn that respect?

191
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:10,210
If I can't have her,

192
00:11:11,100 --> 00:11:12,360
I'll just destroy her.

193
00:11:13,670 --> 00:11:15,830
But I have to be the one to do it.

194
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:17,970
As for anyone else,

195
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,240
whoever lays a finger on her,

196
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,300
I'll come for them.

197
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,080
Alright.

198
00:11:27,870 --> 00:11:28,670
I hear you.

199
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,770
Are you calm now?

200
00:11:47,150 --> 00:11:47,870
Boss,

201
00:11:48,750 --> 00:11:50,480
stop sending people to test me.

202
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,100
I've really...

203
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:54,400
been worn out lately.

204
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:57,720
I know.

205
00:11:59,030 --> 00:12:00,490
You've worked hard enough

206
00:12:00,870 --> 00:12:02,330
setting up the new routes.

207
00:12:02,910 --> 00:12:03,630
Relax.

208
00:12:04,630 --> 00:12:07,030
Old Scorpion's already decided
when he's coming.

209
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,030
Get ready.

210
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:42,800
Leader Yao,

211
00:12:42,820 --> 00:12:44,100
what's so urgent?

212
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,220
Close the door.

213
00:12:45,350 --> 00:12:45,880
Sit down.

214
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:57,280
What is it?

215
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:10,480
What is this?

216
00:13:10,910 --> 00:13:12,200
This is intelligence passed back

217
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,600
by an undercover of mine.

218
00:13:14,870 --> 00:13:15,910
A cargo ship

219
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:19,160
[Oct. 3—closing in at Jingang Wharf]

220
00:13:16,390 --> 00:13:17,550
will dock at Jingang Wharf

221
00:13:17,550 --> 00:13:19,080
on October 3rd.

222
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:21,600
There'll be a large-scale drug deal.

223
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,730
When the time comes,

224
00:13:22,870 --> 00:13:25,870
people from Hengyun Logistics
will pick up the goods.

225
00:13:26,910 --> 00:13:27,840
They have guns.

226
00:13:29,790 --> 00:13:31,100
Is this intel reliable?

227
00:13:31,100 --> 00:13:31,980
Very reliable.

228
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:35,630
Tan.

229
00:13:37,510 --> 00:13:38,710
It's been five years.

230
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:41,550
You have to help me.

231
00:13:41,550 --> 00:13:43,280
Come on, don't say it like that.

232
00:13:43,510 --> 00:13:44,310
Rest assured,

233
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,370
I'll definitely go all out.

234
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:50,080
With approval
from the Provincial Bureau leadership,

235
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:52,240
I'm now going to fully disclose

236
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:53,840
all classified information

237
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:55,950
related to the 8/17 Case.

238
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:57,480
Wait a sec.

239
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:02,720
Go ahead.

240
00:14:04,030 --> 00:14:05,150
Five years ago,

241
00:14:05,910 --> 00:14:07,000
the reason I was able to locate

242
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:09,930
the hideout of the criminal gang
behind the 8/17 Case

243
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:13,090
was because of Jiang Hansheng's help.

244
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:17,340
He'd identified one of them beforehand,

245
00:14:17,780 --> 00:14:19,240
and that person was Qi Yan.

246
00:14:20,040 --> 00:14:21,550
We provoked Qi Yan

247
00:14:21,870 --> 00:14:23,470
to make him give himself away.

248
00:14:23,470 --> 00:14:24,750
At that time, every intersection

249
00:14:24,750 --> 00:14:26,680
in Haizhou had checkpoints set up.

250
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,800
The gang committed the crime

251
00:14:29,050 --> 00:14:30,650
and couldn't leave the city.

252
00:14:30,790 --> 00:14:31,550
So they stayed in

253
00:14:31,550 --> 00:14:33,750
an abandoned warehouse in the suburbs.

254
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:36,550
I was the one who led the team
to carry out the arrest.

255
00:14:36,550 --> 00:14:38,350
The plan was to catch them alive,

256
00:14:38,450 --> 00:14:40,110
but those cornered criminals

257
00:14:40,110 --> 00:14:41,710
put up a desperate struggle.

258
00:14:41,750 --> 00:14:43,150
So during the firefight,

259
00:14:43,660 --> 00:14:45,630
four suspects were killed on the spot,

260
00:14:45,630 --> 00:14:46,920
including Qi Yan.

261
00:14:47,660 --> 00:14:51,910
[Sixth day
after Jiang Hansheng was captured]

262
00:14:51,520 --> 00:14:52,120
Jiang Hansheng,

263
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:52,960
don't shoot!

264
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:53,620
Don't move!

265
00:14:54,220 --> 00:14:55,290
I'm Yao Weihai!

266
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:56,550
Look closely, I'm Yao Weihai!

267
00:14:56,550 --> 00:14:56,910
Don't move!

268
00:14:56,910 --> 00:14:58,120
Officer Jiang!

269
00:14:58,240 --> 00:14:59,360
The police are here.

270
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:01,030
Let's listen to the police, okay?

271
00:15:01,030 --> 00:15:02,000
I surrender.

272
00:15:02,310 --> 00:15:03,610
I surrender, Officer Jiang!

273
00:15:03,610 --> 00:15:04,520
Jiang Hansheng!

274
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:05,590
I'm Yao Weihai!

275
00:15:05,620 --> 00:15:06,440
Officer Jiang,

276
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:07,200
don't do anything rash.

277
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,000
We have the situation under control.

278
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,390
Don't do anything rash!

279
00:15:09,390 --> 00:15:11,550
Look closely! I'm here. Don't be nervous!

280
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:12,480
I'm Yao Weihai!

281
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:14,080
I just want to give this back to you!

282
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:14,960
Listen to the police!

283
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:15,690
Jiang Hansheng!

284
00:15:15,690 --> 00:15:17,000
I really surrender!

285
00:15:17,030 --> 00:15:17,980
Don't get agitated!

286
00:15:17,980 --> 00:15:18,580
Calm down!

287
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:22,270
I will kill you!

288
00:15:23,510 --> 00:15:24,510
Qi Yan!

289
00:15:24,870 --> 00:15:25,750
No!

290
00:15:36,930 --> 00:15:38,150
After that operation,

291
00:15:38,150 --> 00:15:40,280
we continued verifying the identities

292
00:15:40,280 --> 00:15:41,480
of the four deceased.

293
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:44,600
We eventually identified
the real name of one of them:

294
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:45,840
Feng He.

295
00:15:47,510 --> 00:15:48,740
He had a prior record—

296
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:52,220
