for illegal arms trafficking.

297
00:15:52,220 --> 00:15:53,420
By mapping out

298
00:15:53,450 --> 00:15:54,640
Feng He's network,

299
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:57,840
we discovered he had close dealings

300
00:15:58,080 --> 00:15:59,390
with a broker named He Wen.

301
00:15:59,390 --> 00:16:01,390
According to Feng He's associates,

302
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:03,440
He Wen could get his hands on goods

303
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:05,150
that others couldn't get on the market—

304
00:16:05,150 --> 00:16:06,550
drugs, firearms,

305
00:16:06,910 --> 00:16:08,110
wild animals,

306
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:09,540
and even children—

307
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:12,200
available in
both large and small quantities.

308
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,270
He Wen?

309
00:16:13,910 --> 00:16:14,440
Right.

310
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:15,360
Go on.

311
00:16:20,550 --> 00:16:22,950
At the time,
we suspected that behind He Wen

312
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:26,270
there was
an entire criminal trade network.

313
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,320
So, in order to completely take down

314
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:29,580
this crime syndicate,

315
00:16:30,410 --> 00:16:31,240
five years ago, we

316
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:33,400
launched an undercover operation

317
00:16:33,430 --> 00:16:34,630
codenamed Cangfeng.

318
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:37,510
At that time,
He Wen was serving a sentence

319
00:16:37,510 --> 00:16:39,360
at Guhua Prison for attempted murder.

320
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,690
I took that opportunity

321
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:42,820
to have Cangfeng get close to him.

322
00:16:42,960 --> 00:16:45,220
We thought we'd find clues very quickly.

323
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:48,080
But who would've thought...

324
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:51,440
the waters in Haizhou ran this deep?

325
00:16:53,470 --> 00:16:54,760
Once we stepped in,

326
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:57,840
five years passed in the blink of an eye.

327
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:01,670
This...

328
00:17:02,780 --> 00:17:04,970
is the intel Cangfeng sent back?

329
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:05,690
Yes.

330
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:10,550
After five years of
undercover investigation, Cangfeng

331
00:17:10,550 --> 00:17:12,680
has helped us gain a general understanding

332
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:14,680
