that orchestrated the 8/17 gun robbery

333
00:17:14,680 --> 00:17:16,010
and police murder case.

334
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:18,640
They all belong to a crime syndicate

335
00:17:18,770 --> 00:17:20,200
led by Old Scorpion.

336
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:23,750
Old Scorpion's

337
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:26,200
name, age, and appearance

338
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:27,329
remain unknown.

339
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,010
Since the 8/17 Case,

340
00:17:29,110 --> 00:17:30,510
he hasn't shown up again.

341
00:17:30,510 --> 00:17:32,640
He has many branches under his control

342
00:17:33,440 --> 00:17:35,100
operating in various places,

343
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:37,040
