347
00:17:46,350 --> 00:17:47,640
He Wen, He Wu...

348
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:49,680
They're brothers?

349
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:50,480
That's right.

350
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:52,480
Old Scorpion,

351
00:17:53,990 --> 00:17:55,270
He Wen, He Wu,

352
00:17:55,640 --> 00:17:56,440
Feng He—

353
00:17:56,460 --> 00:17:59,320
