a temporary command center.

380
00:19:05,120 --> 00:19:07,440
Leaders from the Provincial Bureau
will be present to oversee the operation.

381
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:08,240
And you

382
00:19:08,910 --> 00:19:11,310
