393
00:20:25,640 --> 00:20:26,160
Dr. Su.

394
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,030
Zhou.

395
00:20:27,820 --> 00:20:29,130
This is Professor Ding.

396
00:20:29,130 --> 00:20:30,260
This is Officer Zhou.

397
00:20:30,260 --> 00:20:30,900
Nice to meet you.

398
00:20:30,900 --> 00:20:31,830
Nice to meet you.

