450
00:22:51,470 --> 00:22:53,330
The case was solved very quickly.

451
00:22:54,130 --> 00:22:55,620
Was it Professor Ding back then too?

452
00:22:55,620 --> 00:22:56,100
Yes.

453
00:22:56,390 --> 00:22:58,110
Professor Ding is my mentor.

454
00:22:58,380 --> 00:22:59,490
He's the nation's

455
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:01,250
