572
00:31:06,550 --> 00:31:07,440
No!

573
00:31:08,230 --> 00:31:08,880
No!

574
00:31:09,070 --> 00:31:09,750
No!

575
00:31:10,170 --> 00:31:10,820
Wait.

576
00:31:10,950 --> 00:31:11,640
Save me.

577
00:31:16,190 --> 00:31:17,320
