I'm sorry.

586
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:36,660
I hit the wrong target.

587
00:32:38,590 --> 00:32:39,310
Sorry.

588
00:32:40,840 --> 00:32:42,080
I didn't mean to.

589
00:32:43,750 --> 00:32:44,950
I'm really sorry.

590
00:32:44,980 --> 00:32:46,380
I didn't do it on purpose.

591
00:32:49,750 --> 00:32:50,350
I'm sorry.

592
00:32:50,510 --> 00:32:51,030
I'm sorry.

593
00:32:51,030 --> 00:32:52,030
I'm really sorry.

594
00:32:53,990 --> 00:32:55,470
I truly didn't mean to.

595
00:32:55,800 --> 00:32:56,430
Sorry.

596
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:28,060
You deliberately provoked me

597
00:33:29,050 --> 00:33:30,310
into coming after you.

598
00:33:32,070 --> 00:33:33,070
Officer Jiang...

599
00:33:35,130 --> 00:33:36,480
Are you challenging me?

600
00:33:38,750 --> 00:33:40,670
Most cops wouldn't act like you.

601
00:33:42,870 --> 00:33:44,200
You're quite unhinged.

602
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:54,320
Can we pause for a moment?

603
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,420
Hansheng made it clear

604
00:33:55,420 --> 00:33:56,400
that unless it reaches a critical point,

605
00:33:56,400 --> 00:33:57,510
we shouldn't interrupt.

606
00:33:57,510 --> 00:33:58,440
Jiang Hansheng,

607
00:33:59,070 --> 00:33:59,960
don't worry.

608
00:34:00,610 --> 00:34:02,000
You're fine now.

609
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:03,550
Relax.

610
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,460
Take a deep breath.

611
00:34:06,470 --> 00:34:08,679
Everything is calm now.

612
00:34:10,670 --> 00:34:11,600
Jiang Hansheng,

613
00:34:12,659 --> 00:34:13,860
do you still remember

614
00:34:14,630 --> 00:34:16,030
why we came here?

615
00:34:17,020 --> 00:34:18,580
Can you still see?

616
00:34:19,230 --> 00:34:19,960
Yes, I can.

617
00:34:20,510 --> 00:34:20,960
Good.

618
00:34:21,590 --> 00:34:23,190
Then let's

619
00:34:23,290 --> 00:34:24,810
carefully look over

620
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:26,920
this entire space once more.

621
00:34:27,780 --> 00:34:28,860
You can

622
00:34:29,480 --> 00:34:31,120
take a look at every corner

623
00:34:32,030 --> 00:34:33,280
and every person.

624
00:34:34,750 --> 00:34:35,310
One.

625
00:34:37,400 --> 00:34:37,960
Two.

626
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:40,630
Three.

627
00:34:42,710 --> 00:34:43,320
Four.

628
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:45,920
Tell me.

629
00:34:48,420 --> 00:34:49,969
What are you counting?

630
00:34:50,670 --> 00:34:51,440
One.

631
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:52,920
Two.

632
00:34:54,320 --> 00:34:54,840
Three.

633
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:56,920
Four.

634
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:58,670
Five.

635
00:34:59,150 --> 00:35:00,230
Wasn't it four?

636
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:03,360
One.

637
00:35:05,110 --> 00:35:05,630
Two.

638
00:35:07,150 --> 00:35:07,760
Three.

639
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:09,550
Four.

640
00:35:11,110 --> 00:35:11,880
Impossible.

641
00:35:13,190 --> 00:35:13,800
Three.

642
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:15,510
Four.

643
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:17,030
Five.

644
00:35:18,740 --> 00:35:19,610
Where is he?

645
00:35:22,100 --> 00:35:23,030
Jiang Hansheng!

646
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,280
Jiang Hansheng,

647
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:26,110
listen to me.

648
00:35:26,570 --> 00:35:27,650
You're very safe!

649
00:35:27,780 --> 00:35:29,650
You've already been rescued!

650
00:35:30,070 --> 00:35:30,780
Listen carefully—

651
00:35:30,780 --> 00:35:31,770
follow my instructions!

652
00:35:31,770 --> 00:35:33,080
Wake up right now!

653
00:35:33,150 --> 00:35:34,190
Wake up now!

654
00:35:40,880 --> 00:35:41,940
Alright, alright.

655
00:35:42,470 --> 00:35:43,400
You're okay now.

656
00:35:46,030 --> 00:35:47,280
Let's take a break.

657
00:35:51,400 --> 00:35:52,590
Can we go in now?

658
00:35:53,330 --> 00:35:53,890
Yes.

659
00:35:58,100 --> 00:35:58,860
How are you doing?

660
00:35:58,860 --> 00:36:00,000
There weren't four of them.

661
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:00,570
Are you sure?

662
00:36:00,570 --> 00:36:01,900
I saw five meal boxes

663
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:03,130
and five pairs of chopsticks.

664
00:36:03,130 --> 00:36:04,740
But all the files you gave me

665
00:36:05,070 --> 00:36:07,000
indicated there were four people.

666
00:36:43,080 --> 00:36:44,340
There were two Qi Yans.

667
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:12,870
Team 1, in position.

668
00:37:12,870 --> 00:37:14,000
Team 2, in position.

669
00:37:14,030 --> 00:37:15,160
Team 3, in position.

670
00:37:15,550 --> 00:37:16,610
Lock on the target.

671
00:37:22,110 --> 00:37:23,760
The target ship is expected to dock

672
00:37:23,760 --> 00:37:24,820
within 10 minutes.

673
00:37:25,030 --> 00:37:26,030
Once the deal is done,

674
00:37:26,030 --> 00:37:27,030
move in immediately.

675
00:37:27,030 --> 00:37:27,710
Copy that!

676
00:37:30,710 --> 00:37:31,590
Chief Tan,

677
00:37:31,610 --> 00:37:32,730
Professor Jiang is looking for you.

678
00:37:32,730 --> 00:37:34,060
It seems rather urgent.

679
00:37:41,190 --> 00:37:42,630
Director Lu, Commander Liu,

680
00:37:42,630 --> 00:37:44,000
something's come up.
I'll step out for a moment.

681
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:44,640
Go ahead.

682
00:37:44,920 --> 00:37:45,480
Yes, sir!

683
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:48,090
Are you sure?

684
00:37:48,550 --> 00:37:49,280
I'm sure.

685
00:37:49,920 --> 00:37:51,510
The man who died five years ago

686
00:37:51,510 --> 00:37:52,310
was not Qi Yan.

687
00:37:52,670 --> 00:37:53,510
And we've just checked with

688
00:37:53,510 --> 00:37:55,550
the forensic examiner
who handled the case at the time.

689
00:37:55,550 --> 00:37:57,030
He said that on Qi Yan's body,

690
00:37:57,030 --> 00:37:58,590
apart from the gunshot wound
between the eyebrows,

691
00:37:58,590 --> 00:37:59,440
there were

692
00:37:59,590 --> 00:38:01,800
no blunt force trauma marks
anywhere on the head.

693
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:03,330
That doesn't add up either.

694
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:04,930
Where is Leader Yao?

695
00:38:05,040 --> 00:38:06,840
I haven't been able to reach him.

696
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:07,920
He's on a mission.

697
00:38:08,510 --> 00:38:10,170
Is it related to the 8/17 Case?

698
00:38:14,710 --> 00:38:17,170
Leader Yao received reliable intelligence

699
00:38:17,190 --> 00:38:18,920
that tonight at Jingang Wharf,

700
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:21,410
there will be a large-scale drug deal.

701
00:38:21,480 --> 00:38:22,800
The biggest mastermind behind

702
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:24,460
the 8/17 Case crime syndicate

703
00:38:24,670 --> 00:38:26,470
will be there in person tonight.

704
00:38:26,710 --> 00:38:27,760
So Leader Yao

705
00:38:28,030 --> 00:38:28,900
personally led the team

706
00:38:28,900 --> 00:38:31,000
to Jingang Wharf to carry out the arrest.

707
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:31,660
It's a trap.

708
00:38:32,400 --> 00:38:33,400
No matter who the source was

709
00:38:33,400 --> 00:38:34,670
or what intel they gave us,

710
00:38:34,670 --> 00:38:36,400
it's highly likely to be a trap.

711
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:38,800
Why would Leader Yao
personally lead the team?

712
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:39,760
Could they be using

713
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:40,670
this so-called mastermind

714
00:38:40,670 --> 00:38:41,930
to lure Leader Yao out?

715
00:38:42,510 --> 00:38:44,230
Qi Yan held significant influence

716
00:38:44,230 --> 00:38:45,480
within the 8/17 Case crime syndicate.

717
00:38:45,480 --> 00:38:46,800
If he's still alive,

718
00:38:47,080 --> 00:38:47,920
he would definitely participate

719
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:48,810
in such a deal.

720
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:50,670
Back then, it was Leader Yao

721
00:38:50,670 --> 00:38:52,190
who led the team to arrest them.

722
00:38:52,190 --> 00:38:53,190
It's very likely

723
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:55,130
a trap they set to get back at us!

724
00:38:58,070 --> 00:38:59,530
The deal is about to start.

725
00:39:04,070 --> 00:39:04,670
Bai Yang!

726
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:05,370
Yes, sir.

727
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:07,000
Where is He Wu?

728
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:09,360
He hasn't moved
since he got to the Ruixiang Hotel.

729
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:10,550
He's having dinner right now.

730
00:39:10,550 --> 00:39:12,000
Put me through to Leader Yao.

731
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,030
Leader Yao, Leader Yao,

732
00:39:13,030 --> 00:39:14,160
this is Tan Shiming.

733
00:39:14,190 --> 00:39:15,030
What's going on?

734
00:39:15,030 --> 00:39:16,490
There are a lot of unknowns

735
00:39:16,550 --> 00:39:17,950
in tonight's operation.

736
00:39:18,230 --> 00:39:19,320
Listen to me,

737
00:39:19,710 --> 00:39:20,670
Qi Yan...

738
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:22,800
might not be dead.

739
00:39:23,260 --> 00:39:24,690
He's very likely to appear at

740
00:39:24,690 --> 00:39:25,820
tonight's deal.

741
00:39:26,150 --> 00:39:27,710
Qi Yan is still alive?

742
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:29,480
I don't have time to explain.

743
00:39:29,710 --> 00:39:30,400
In short,

744
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:31,980
Professor Jiang's analysis suggests

745
00:39:31,980 --> 00:39:34,910
that the person
who died five years ago wasn't Qi Yan.

746
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:36,230
Tonight's deal

747
00:39:36,400 --> 00:39:38,070
is likely a trap set by him.

748
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:39,400
So far,

749
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:40,840
He Wu hasn't arrived at the wharf.

750
00:39:40,840 --> 00:39:42,700
That alone is highly suspicious.

751
00:39:47,840 --> 00:39:49,570
Chief Tan, the boat has docked.

752
00:39:54,760 --> 00:39:55,440
Leader Yao!

753
00:39:56,840 --> 00:39:58,880
Compared to the deal,

754
00:39:58,920 --> 00:40:00,710
Qi Yan is more interested in the police.

755
00:40:00,710 --> 00:40:02,480
Professor Jiang analyzed it the same way.

756
00:40:02,480 --> 00:40:05,080
Do we still proceed with
tonight's operation?

757
00:40:10,990 --> 00:40:12,190
It's been five years.

758
00:40:12,390 --> 00:40:14,380
We've finally mapped out

759
00:40:14,480 --> 00:40:15,880
the entire Jin-Hai Line.

760
00:40:16,650 --> 00:40:19,310
Old Scorpion has been in hiding
all these years,

761
00:40:19,440 --> 00:40:21,400
and now he's finally showing himself.

762
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:22,030
Yes.

763
00:40:23,480 --> 00:40:24,960
This is our only chance.

764
00:40:27,280 --> 00:40:28,190
When it's over,

765
00:40:28,500 --> 00:40:29,620
I can go home.

766
00:40:33,590 --> 00:40:35,000
I understand the situation.

767
00:40:35,000 --> 00:40:36,400
Send two more police units

768
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:37,730
to the wharf for backup.

769
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:39,120
Let's proceed as planned.

770
00:40:39,120 --> 00:40:39,760
Copy that.

771
00:40:44,590 --> 00:40:46,030
According to informants,

772
00:40:46,030 --> 00:40:48,480
the target ship docking at Jingang Wharf

773
00:40:48,590 --> 00:40:50,360
is carrying a large quantity of drugs.

774
00:40:50,360 --> 00:40:51,960
The buyer coming for the deal

775
00:40:52,070 --> 00:40:53,550
is a criminal syndicate
that has been hiding

776
00:40:53,550 --> 00:40:55,350
in the Jin-Hai region for years.

777
00:40:55,590 --> 00:40:56,550
Their leader

778
00:40:57,280 --> 00:40:58,710
is the drug kingpin our police

779
00:40:58,710 --> 00:41:00,640
have been pursuing for a long time—

780
00:41:01,070 --> 00:41:02,070
known by the alias

781
00:41:02,440 --> 00:41:03,240
Old Scorpion.

782
00:41:03,360 --> 00:41:04,620
His specific identity

783
00:41:05,070 --> 00:41:06,510
and physical features are unknown.

784
00:41:06,510 --> 00:41:07,970
We only know his nickname.

785
00:41:08,070 --> 00:41:09,800
Proceed with extreme caution.

786
00:41:10,810 --> 00:41:11,560
Leaders,

787
00:41:11,900 --> 00:41:13,260
I'm heading to the scene immediately.

788
00:41:13,260 --> 00:41:13,890
Go ahead.

789
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:14,740
Leave this to us.

790
00:41:14,740 --> 00:41:15,270
Yes, sir!

791
00:41:20,750 --> 00:41:22,150
Senior, why are you here?

792
00:41:22,630 --> 00:41:23,690
Same reason as you.

793
00:41:40,150 --> 00:41:41,110
Don't stop me.

794
00:41:41,590 --> 00:41:42,550
Trust me,

795
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:43,670
okay?

796
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:02,840
Be careful.

797
00:42:17,200 --> 00:42:18,190
Keep your eyes on the target

798
00:42:18,190 --> 00:42:18,960
and report immediately.

799
00:42:18,960 --> 00:42:19,940
Do not act alone...

800
00:42:19,940 --> 00:42:21,110
Senior, which car should I be in?

801
00:42:21,110 --> 00:42:22,510
Junior, why are you here?

802
00:42:25,000 --> 00:42:26,330
What are you doing here?

803
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:27,480
Who told you to come?

804
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:28,110
Sir,

805
00:42:28,310 --> 00:42:29,710
Officer Zhou Jin requests
to join the operation.

806
00:42:29,710 --> 00:42:30,640
Stay out of this.

807
00:42:30,670 --> 00:42:31,320
Sir,

808
00:42:31,480 --> 00:42:33,150
Officer Zhou Jin requests
to join the operation!

809
00:42:33,150 --> 00:42:35,140
I've been waiting for this day
for five years.

810
00:42:35,140 --> 00:42:36,470
Please grant approval.

811
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:38,440
Mentor,

812
00:42:38,440 --> 00:42:41,370
if you really can't stop her,
just let her come along.

813
00:42:41,840 --> 00:42:42,700
How about this?

814
00:42:43,030 --> 00:42:44,110
You'll go with the team tracking He Wu.

815
00:42:44,110 --> 00:42:44,730
Mentor!

816
00:42:44,750 --> 00:42:46,030
Don't say I didn't give you a chance.

817
00:42:46,030 --> 00:42:48,510
And don't say
I didn't give you an assignment!

818
00:42:48,510 --> 00:42:49,400
Are you all ready?

819
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:50,070
Ready.

820
00:42:50,070 --> 00:42:50,870
Then move out!

821
00:42:51,420 --> 00:42:51,920
Junior,

822
00:42:51,940 --> 00:42:53,470
you go with Zhao Ping's car.

823
00:42:53,510 --> 00:42:54,150
Be good.

824
00:43:02,150 --> 00:43:02,800
Zhao Ping,

825
00:43:02,800 --> 00:43:03,480
stop the car!

826
00:43:03,480 --> 00:43:04,110
Senior.

827
00:43:04,110 --> 00:43:04,760
Let me in!

828
00:43:04,760 --> 00:43:05,240
Get in.
